FROM --platform=$BUILDPLATFORM golang:1.26-alpine AS builder
ARG TARGETOS TARGETARCH
WORKDIR /src
COPY go.mod go.sum ./
RUN go mod download
COPY . .
RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=$TARGETOS GOARCH=$TARGETARCH \
    go build -ldflags="-s -w" -o /bbrokerd ./cmd/bbrokerd

FROM alpine:3.20
RUN addgroup -S bbroker && adduser -S bbroker -G bbroker
USER bbroker
COPY --from=builder /bbrokerd /bbrokerd
ENTRYPOINT ["/bbrokerd"]
